News.Title: RNFI Services Partners With IndusInd Bank
News.Summary: RNFI Services announces strategic partnership with IndusInd Bank to launch international remittance services using AD-II license, expanding financial service offerings.

News.Title: RNFI Services Engaged by Hero FinCorp Limited for Specialized Services
News.Summary: RNFI Services has been contracted as a service provider to deliver specialized services to Hero FinCorp Limited (HFCL). RNFI Services is a company with a market capitalization of 651 crore rupees.

News.Title: RNFI Services Appointed as Corporate Business Correspondent for Jio Payments Bank
News.Summary: RNFI Services has been engaged as a corporate business correspondent for Jio Payments Bank. This partnership is likely to expand RNFI's financial services reach and potentially contribute to Jio Payments Bank's customer base and service offerings.
